In a message dated 4/8/02 6:06:44 AM, homeschoolmd@... writes:

<< I haven't thought out the details but maybe we could put our heads
together and come up with something. Anyone? >>

Maybe someone can find us an already-established video library for public
borrowing. The mailing of videos isn't easy--usually involving going to the
post office. And the cost of them means if one is lost the owner will be
grumpy.

I'd much prefer not to start anything that will produce something to fight or
complain about.

Sandra
